  "instruction": "A local concept brief is already available in Chrome at file:///home/user/Desktop/launch_story_lab_brief.html. Use VS Code to build /home/user/Desktop/launch_story_lab into a richer generative UI story page from the provided story.json and assets/launch-mark.svg. Create index.html, styles.css, app.js, and manifest.json. Build a storytelling page with main#story-app, section#hero, section#insight-grid, section#milestones, canvas#sentimentChart, and dialog#noteDialog. Load story.json with fetch(), render 4 insight cards and 3 milestone items from the data, use the local SVG mark in the hero or header area, and implement an interaction that opens the dialog or toggles a detail panel when a milestone button is clicked. Draw a bar or column chart for the sentiment series on the canvas. Manifest must set project to launch-story-lab, theme to orchid-night, chartType to bar, dataSource to story.json, and previewPort to 8126. Start a local preview server and finish with Chrome open at http://127.0.0.1:8126/index.html.",
